title: The Best Banana Pudding # the recipe name/title
category: Sweets and Drinks # appetizers, soups and salads, side dishes, main courses, sweets and drinks
shortdescription: A true southern dessert, perfect for summertime picnics. # a brief description of your recipe
ingredients: 
1 large tub of Cool Whip - 16 oz.  If you prefer you can make a stabilized whipping cream that has cream cheese. 
5 oz (1 large box) Vanilla instant pudding mix - you can use your own recipe or get it from the store
11 oz (1 box) of vanilla wafers 
14oz - 1 can sweetened condensed milk
7 bananas
Milk (use recipe amount from instant pudding)
# list of ingredients
directions: # detailed directions
prepare pudding according to recipe on box
combine pudding, condensed milk, and cool whip - mix well
in a large bowl layer in the following order: pudding mix, wafers, and bananas, until you use all the pudding (about 3 layers)
top with remaining wafers
refrigerate for 1 hour
serve
